This is Debianized package of wxMEdit.

wxMEdit is a cross-platform Text/Hex Editor.
wxMEdit is an improved version of MadEdit which has been discontinued.

wxMEdit supports many useful functions, e.g. Bookmark, 
Syntax Highlightings, Word Wrap, Encodings, Column/Hex Modes, 
WordCount and Updates Checking.

wxMEdit is a continually maintained text/hex editor with bug fixes, 
improvements and refactor.

The original source code for this package can be downloaded from
wxMEdit website or https://github.com/wxMEdit/wxMEdit .

Website: http://wxmedit.github.io/ .

